主要翻译
 
moron n pejorative (idiot)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 傻子 shǎ zi  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 笨蛋 shǎ zi ，bèn dàn 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 笨蛋 shǎ zi ，bèn dàn 
 -- Seth yelled at the moron at the restaurant who brought him the wrong order.
 -- 餐厅的那个笨蛋给赛斯上错了菜，惹得赛斯对他大喊大叫。

